carnival or a party or anything like that.

00:02:27.740 --> 00:02:30.940
[Music]

00:02:30.940 --> 00:02:31.920
It tastes pretty much the same.

00:02:31.920 --> 00:02:34.280
And, of course, one of
the hallmarks of cotton candy

00:02:34.280 --> 00:02:36.320
is that it dissolves 
pretty much instantly

00:02:36.320 --> 00:02:37.480
once you put in your mouth.

00:02:37.480 --> 00:02:43.020
